subsection.p:
soapUI Pro adds the possibility to have a central library of Groovy Classes that can be accessed from
		any script within soapUI, which can be useful for centralizing common tasks and functionality and for 
		creating soapUI extensions. Use as follows;

subsection.source:
package soapui.demo

class Greet 
{
   def name
   def log
   
   Greet(who, log) 
   { 
      name = who;
      this.log = log 
   }
 
   def salute() { log.info "Hello $name" }
 
   def static salute( who, log ) { log.info "Hello again $who!" }
}

subsection.p:
